item.title: Hello, World
item.description: I’ve decided I should finally make a little website just for random thoughts and links. I haven’t put a ton of thought into what this all will look like, but i’m working on it, hopefully I’ll actually keep up with this thing. For now, this site is made with Hugo, because I’ve used it before, and it’s quite easy to make something simple and nice, and in theory it’ll be easy to jump into it and update it.
